ession ID 参数遍历行为。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/2000-05/0160.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1203","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19914","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/30c3a896d257362f7419b0c772be2f3dd063ccaa/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0397.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0397","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-2000-0397.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d0a8c476da89b37a2bbb6193b7964b10d03aff75/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0397.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-xmvv-4vx6-5fqj/GHSA-xmvv-4vx6-5fqj.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/39f1db26eec9899ab2f8110ab3b45424c6fe9ec2/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0397.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152400_152500.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--6180dab5-9713-49ee-9b3a-c1812cdb1fb1.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/839e2559933f5ff6cd50b4768fd382827d790668/2000.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0328.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0330","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0330.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0400","title":"Microsoft Active Movie ActiveX 控件任意文件下载漏洞","description":"Microsoft Active Movie ActiveX 控件在 Internet Explorer 5 中存在输入验证不当漏洞，未对可下载文件类型进行有效限制。远程攻击者可通过电子邮件或新闻组帖子中嵌入特制的编码内容，诱使用户访问恶意页面，从而在用户系统上下载任意类型文件。该漏洞影响使用 Internet Explorer 5 浏览器的 Microsoft Windows 系统，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。用户可升级浏览器或禁用相关 ActiveX 控件进行防护。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0400"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"2000-05-13T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:38.210","remediation":"建议立即安装 Microsoft 2000 年 6 月发布的 Internet Explorer 安全更新（MS00-027），升级至 IE 5.01 或更高版本。如无法升级，可通过注册表设置 Active Movie Control 的 Kill Bit（CLSID: 05589FA0-C356-11CE-BF01-00AA0055595A），在 HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\SOFTWARE\\Microsoft\\Internet Explorer\\ActiveX Compatibility 下新建 Compatibility Flags 为 0x400 以禁用该控件。同时将 Internet 区域 ActiveX 安全级别设为\"高\"并禁用\"对未标记为安全的 ActiveX 控件进行初始化和脚本化\"。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=95868514521257&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1221","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19928","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/30c3a896d257362f7419b0c772be2f3dd063ccaa/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0400.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d0a8c476da89b37a2bbb6193b7964b10d03aff75/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0400.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0400","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0400.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/39f1db26eec9899ab2f8110ab3b45424c6fe9ec2/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0400.json","https://github.com/fkie-cad/nvd-json-data-feeds/blob/35c40c2c96029682f9c3da862749763b6c97e1fb/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-04xx/CVE-2000-0400.json","https://github.com/opencve/opencve-kb/blob/1dbe320292d59a7e991f72ba1744c84debd60371/2000/CVE-2000-0400.json","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelist-dev/blob/5b8fbb570438e8094550205589cc6f1d122acc94/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0400.json","https://github.com/CyberSecAI/cve_info/blob/03b7e36424574a3a9ba5fd13480a326b666a1046/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0400.json","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-nvd/blob/b596b847a09ba1b9204d0c3431cee40f55c25b2e/api/2000/CVE-2000-0400.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0330.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/2000/EXP-AVE-2000-0330.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0330.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0334","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0334.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0407","title":"Sun Solaris netpr 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Solaris 系统中的 netpr 程序存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，本地攻击者可通过向 -p 选项提交超长参数触发该漏洞，导致缓冲区溢出并能够以 root 权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 Solaris 2.6、7.0 及 8.0 版本，攻击者需具有本地用户身份登录系统后方可利用此漏洞，成功利用后可完全控制受影响系统。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0407"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"2000-05-12T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:39.103","remediation":"安装 Sun 官方补丁 (Patch ID 106541-02 或更新版本) 修复 netpr 缓冲区溢出漏洞。如无法打补丁，可移除 netpr 程序的 setuid 权限作为临时缓解措施：`chmod u-s /usr/lib/print/netpr`。限制本地用户对受影响系统的交互式访问也可降低利用风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/2000-05/0141.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1200","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19911","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/30c3a896d257362f7419b0c772be2f3dd063ccaa/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0407.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0407","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-2000-0407.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d0a8c476da89b37a2bbb6193b7964b10d03aff75/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0407.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-x2j2-wmj4-cgv8/GHSA-x2j2-wmj4-cgv8.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152400_152500.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_5.list.dict","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/39f1db26eec9899ab2f8110ab3b45424c6fe9ec2/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0407.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001372.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0334.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0334.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0335","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0335.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0408","title":"Microsoft IIS 4.0/5.0 文件扩展名拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft IIS 4.0 及 5.0 存在畸形文件扩展名解析拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者无需身份认证，通过向目标服务器发送包含大量文件扩展名的超长复杂 URL，可触发 IIS 处理扩展名数据时发生异常，导致 Web 服务进程崩溃，造成拒绝服务。攻击条件简单，仅需发送特制 HTTP 请求即可实现。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0408"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"2000-05-11T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:39.220","remediation":"建议立即安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS00-023 提供的补丁，或升级至 IIS 6.0 及以上版本。IIS 4.0/5.0 已停止支持，长期方案是升级到受支持的 Windows Server 版本并使用 IIS 8.0 或更高版本；临时缓解措施可在 URLScan 工具中配置拒绝包含过多文件扩展名的请求。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.microsoft.com/technet/support/kb.asp?ID=260205","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1190","http://www.ussrback.com/labs40.html","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/2000/ms00-030","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19907","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/b4f1378756fd26f414d09a97dc81126672830951/2000/CVE-2000-0408.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/30c3a896d257362f7419b0c772be2f3dd063ccaa/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0408.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0408","https://github.com/ARPSyndicate/suricata-vedas/blob/fe24794ad36564b5bbc7c69101525011387b8650/2000/CVE-2000-0408.rules","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/115c94bd1da3cc18977d652d6e78c9f4a5dfc13b/data/year/2000.txt","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d0a8c476da89b37a2bbb6193b7964b10d03aff75/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0408.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/2000/CVE-2000-0408.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-wx3j-8h4r-qj57/GHSA-wx3j-8h4r-qj57.json","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/acunetix/vulnerabilities/vdb/2000/0xxx/cve-2000-0408.yaml","https://github.com/chihsuan/search-engine/blob/9dcdd3e644469883f53565740f0ba8ff617c5120/Data/E99D88C1-C798-40D7-BB8C-47E6405B9469.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0335.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0335.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0339","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0339.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0411","title":"Matt Wright FormMail CGI 环境变量泄露漏洞","description":"Matt Wright 开发的 FormMail CGI 脚本 1.6/1.7/1.8 版本存在环境变量泄露漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向 env_report 参数提交恶意请求，导致服务器环境变量（如路径信息、系统配置等敏感数据）被泄露。攻击者无需身份认证即可利用该漏洞，有助于后续深入攻击。该漏洞影响广泛使用 FormMail 的 Web 服务器。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0411"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"2000-05-10T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:39.580","remediation":"立即停止使用 Matt Wright 的 FormMail 1.6/1.7/1.8 版本，该脚本已停止维护且存在多个已知漏洞。建议迁移至社区维护的 FormMail 分支（如 GitHub 上的 fordnox/FormMail-Clone）或使用现代替代方案（如 CGI::FormMail）。如无法立即替换，可编辑 FormMail 源码，删除或注释掉处理 env_report 参数的相关代码段，并在 Web 服务器（Apache/Nginx）层面限制对 FormMail CGI 脚本的访问来源。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/2000-05/0125.html","http://www.perfectotech.com/blackwatchlabs/vul5_10.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1187","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19906","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/24df5d59670dfe04b9c86de11fa86df63c0d28f7/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0411.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0411","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-2000-0411.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/d0a8c476da89b37a2bbb6193b7964b10d03aff75/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0411.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-gggj-8j7g-cpwh/GHSA-gggj-8j7g-cpwh.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/39f1db26eec9899ab2f8110ab3b45424c6fe9ec2/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0411.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152400_152500.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_3.list.dict","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001364.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0339.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0295","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0295.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0304","title":"Microsoft IIS 4.0/5.0 HTR 请求拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft IIS 4.0 和 5.0 的 IISADMPWD 虚拟目录组件中存在输入验证缺陷，远程攻击者可通过向 inetinfo.exe 发送特制的畸形 HTR 请求（Undelimited .HTR Request），触发解析器异常而导致目标系统拒绝服务。该漏洞影响安装了 IISADMPWD 虚拟目录的 IIS 服务器，无需身份认证即可远程利用，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0304"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-05-10T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:26.273","remediation":"安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS00-028 对应补丁，或删除 IISADMPWD 虚拟目录并移除 .htr 脚本映射。如无法打补丁，建议在 IIS 管理器中删除 .htr 应用程序映射，或升级至更高版本 IIS（6.0+）以彻底规避此漏洞。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1191","http://xforce.iss.net/alerts/advise52.php3","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/2000/ms00-031","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/b4f1378756fd26f414d09a97dc81126672830951/2000/CVE-2000-0304.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e25ede9c3545efaa8ff0b393e30e48edb07502a8/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0304.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0304","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/2000.txt","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/c1321b1a6b0cb3a4c18f791e2c8443742c0cb0b0/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0304.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/2000/CVE-2000-0304.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-7qq3-2c7j-qq7w/GHSA-7qq3-2c7j-qq7w.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/web-iis.rules","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0304.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0295.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0338","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0338.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0409","title":"Netscape Communicator 证书导入符号链接漏洞","description":"Netscape Communicator 4.73及更早版本在导入新证书时存在符号链接跟随漏洞。当用户导入证书时，程序会跟随/tmp目录下的符号链接，导致本地攻击者可以利用此漏洞覆盖目标用户的任意文件，造成信息泄露或系统破坏。攻击者需要本地访问权限，利用难度较高。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0409"],"sources":["cve","exploitdb"],"published":"2000-05-10","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级到Netscape Communicator 4.73以上版本，或限制本地用户对/tmp目录的写权限，避免符号链接攻击。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T05:00:14.520880898+00:00","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/2000-05/0126.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1201"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0338.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0318","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0318.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0384","title":"Intel NetStructure 7110/7180 未记录密码漏洞","description":"Intel NetStructure 7110 和 7180 设备存在未记录的后门账户漏洞（servnow、root、wizard），其密码可通过设备的 MAC 地址推算得出。远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过网络访问目标设备，利用 MAC 地址推导出后门账户密码，从而获取设备的 root 权限，完全控制受影响设备。该漏洞 CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0384"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"2000-05-08T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:36.250","remediation":"立即通过 Web 管理界面或串口登录设备，修改 servnow、root、wizard 三个内置账户的默认密码为强随机密码；如不需远程管理，在防火墙上限制仅可信 IP 能访问设备的管理端口（默认 80/TCP、23/TCP）；若业务允许，可直接禁用 servnow 和 wizard 这两个非必要账户。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://216.188.41.136/","http://www.l0pht.com/advisories/ipivot7180.html","http://www.lopht.com/advisories/ipivot7110.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1182","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1183","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19904","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/b4f1378756fd26f414d09a97dc81126672830951/2000/CVE-2000-0384.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d00c4bdddf18e05c46df568e8ae91e7912ce321c/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0384.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0384","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/2000/CVE-2000-0384.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0384.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-765g-qxmj-pjrx/GHSA-765g-qxmj-pjrx.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x2000/1182/info.html","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--7dec9782-ea7f-4bc5-b055-bb8934ad2691.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_3.list.dict"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0318.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0341","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0341.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0413","title":"Microsoft FrontPage 2000 IIS 4.0/5.0 Server Extensions 物理路径泄露漏洞","description":"Microsoft IIS 4.0/5.0 的 FrontPage 服务器扩展中 shtml.exe 程序存在路径泄露漏洞。远程攻击者可通过请求不存在的 HTML、HTM、ASP 或 SHTML 文件，触发错误消息返回服务器物理路径信息，导致系统目录结构等敏感信息泄露。该漏洞有助于攻击者进一步探测目标环境，为后续攻击提供情报支持，影响运行 IIS 4.0/5.0 及 FrontPage 2000 扩展的 Windows 服务器。此漏洞无需身份认证即可远程利用，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0413"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"2000-05-06T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:39.827","remediation":"升级到受支持的 Windows Server 版本（如 Windows Server 2003+ 的 IIS 6.0 或更高版本），FrontPage 服务器扩展已不再维护，建议迁移至现代 Web 发布方案。如无法升级，可在 IIS 管理器中删除 shtml.exe 的脚本映射，或通过 URLScan 工具过滤包含 shtml.exe 的请求路径作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/2000-05/0084.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1174","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19897","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/b4f1378756fd26f414d09a97dc81126672830951/2000/CVE-2000-0413.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/24df5d59670dfe04b9c86de11fa86df63c0d28f7/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0413.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0413","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0413.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/2000/CVE-2000-0413.md","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/frontpage_shtml.nasl","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-jx68-8j6j-8v87/GHSA-jx68-8j6j-8v87.json","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/invicti/vulnerabilities/db/vulnerabilities/vdb/2000/0xxx/cve-2000-0413.yaml","https://github.com/ivanitlearning/CTF-Repos/blob/b5364388a861fc7457409d494a9d075d73e7867e/Vulnhub/SkyTower/Web-scan.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/39f1db26eec9899ab2f8110ab3b45424c6fe9ec2/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0413.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0341.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/2000/EXP-AVE-2000-0341.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0341.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0348","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0348.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0426","title":"UltraScripts UltraBoard 1.6 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"UltraBoard 1.6 及部分其他版本存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者可通过在 Session 参数中引用\"UltraBoard\"字符串，触发 UltraBoard 不断 fork 自身进程副本，消耗服务器系统资源，导致服务不可用。该漏洞攻击复杂度低，无需身份认证即可远程利用。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0426"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"2000-05-05T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:42.443","remediation":"UltraBoard 1.6 及更早版本已停止维护，官方不再提供补丁。建议立即迁移至其他仍在维护的论坛系统（如 phpBB、Discourse 等）。若暂时无法迁移，可在 Web 服务器（如 Apache）层面添加 RewriteRule 过滤包含 UltraBoard 字样的 Session 参数请求，或在应用入口处对 Session 参数进行正则校验，拒绝包含 UltraBoard 的异常请求，以缓解 fork 耗尽服务器资源的风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/2000-05/0059.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1175","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19899","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/24df5d59670dfe04b9c86de11fa86df63c0d28f7/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0426.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0426","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-2000-0426.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/228df6a85079f5c6b1ecdfb3d41be685458438ef/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0426.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/4544d3857250fe21711ce8febf38e8822729678f/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-6fq7-3q96-vw9x/GHSA-6fq7-3q96-vw9x.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/39f1db26eec9899ab2f8110ab3b45424c6fe9ec2/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0426.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152400_152500.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001354.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--2dbce7bd-880a-4923-8153-39399e9a1deb.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0348.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0344","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0344.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0423","title":"NetWin DNews CGI 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"NetWin DNews 5.3 服务器的 DNEWSWEB CGI 程序存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者通过向 group、cmd、utag 等参数提交超长字符串，可触发缓冲区溢出并在服务器上执行任意命令。该漏洞影响 NetWin DNews 5.3 及更早版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可通过 HTTP 请求远程利用，危害严重。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0423"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"2000-05-05T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:42.067","remediation":"NetWin DNews 5.3 已停止维护且不再发布安全更新，建议立即迁移至其他受支持的 Usenet 新闻服务器软件（如 INN 或 Leafnode）。如无法迁移，须移除 DNEWSWEB CGI 可执行文件的 SUID 权限并在 Web 服务器层面限制对 CGI 脚本的访问来源 IP；同时避免将 group、cmd、utag 等参数直接传递给用户输入。该版本已无官方补丁，继续使用风险极高。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=95764950403250&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1172","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19895","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/24df5d59670dfe04b9c86de11fa86df63c0d28f7/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0423.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0423","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/470a5f1c0d1bd36cd0a6327cda49cf96a1474588/content/CVE-2000-0423.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/228df6a85079f5c6b1ecdfb3d41be685458438ef/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0423.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/4544d3857250fe21711ce8febf38e8822729678f/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-998v-2qg9-284c/GHSA-998v-2qg9-284c.json","https://github.com/xqcyberscore/nvt/blob/978f6a9acb495d7d669239530ffe6da5d631f4da/pre2008/dangerous_cgis.nasl","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0423.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_4.list.dict","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x2000/1172/info.html","https://github.com/akabe1/windows_exploit_dowser/blob/11b24e36173cd382721db28581e575faf687d06b/cve_from_exploitdb_website.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0344.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0316","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0316.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0381","title":"Gossamer Threads DBMan 信息泄露漏洞","description":"Gossamer Threads DBMan 2.0.4 的 db.cgi CGI 脚本存在信息泄露漏洞。远程攻击者通过在 db 参数中引用一个不存在的数据库文件，即可触发 CGI 错误消息，该错误消息会将环境变量与系统配置信息（包括本地文档根目录路径、服务器管理员账户名、Web 服务器软件类型及操作系统平台等敏感数据）泄露给未授权用户。该漏洞利用无需身份认证，攻击者可远程发起探测，影响所有以默认配置运行 DBMan 2.0.4 的 Web 服务器，CVSS v2 评分为 6.4。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.4,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0381"],"sources":["cve","exploitdb"],"published":"2000-05-05T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:35.887","remediation":"立即升级 DBMan 至厂商发布的最新安全版本或官方补丁。如暂时无法升级，应在 Web 服务器配置中限制对 db.cgi 脚本的访问权限，仅允许受信任的 IP 地址调用，并在脚本入口处对 db 参数进行严格校验，拒绝非预期值。同时移除或修改 CGI 脚本中泄露环境变量的调试输出逻辑，可在 .htaccess 中配置认证访问或直接禁用该 CGI 脚本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/2000-05/0067.html","http://www.perfectotech.com/blackwatchlabs/vul5_05.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1178","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19903","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/712a40967986b700313860b08048435be4fa9839/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0381.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0381","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/1fe9b156eeeb72b8f8baa50bbe7bc0d9806e8c64/content/CVE-2000-0381.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24512263eb77d6af2cecd67bd2460f761fc94bea/CVE/data/2000/CVE-2000-0381.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/cdfc8886d71af7ef3bdab3e4db46753ff8af6538/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-xgg5-44qv-95wx/GHSA-xgg5-44qv-95wx.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/sid-msg.map","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0381.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_152300_152400.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001352.txt","https://github.com/entrysky/mageni/blob/c58dcc9bc43b7fb267bb10a8083ada356fbc81d1/plugins/pre2008/dbman_cgi.nasl"],"poc_urls":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19903"],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2000/POC-AVE-2000-0316.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/2000/EXP-AVE-2000-0316.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-2000-0316.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2000-0350","file_name":"2000/AVE-2000-0350.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2000-0427","title":"Aladdin Knowledge Systems eToken 3.3.3 PIN提取漏洞","description":"Aladdin Knowledge Systems eToken 3.3.3 设备存在 PIN 码提取漏洞，具有物理访问权限的攻击者可通过直接操作设备 EEPROM 重置 PIN 码，从而绕过身份验证机制获取敏感信息。该漏洞源于 EEPROM 存储保护不足，攻击者无需知道原所有者 PIN 即可完成重置，影响 eToken 3.3.3 版本，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-2000-0427"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"2000-05-04T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:51:42.583","remediation":"立即停止使用 Aladdin eToken 3.3.3，该产品已停止技术支持超过 20 年。迁移至 Thales SafeNet eToken 系列（如 eToken PRO 或 eToken 5110），新硬件在 EEPROM 层面实现了 PIN 防篡改保护。在迁移完成前，将 eToken 存放于物理安全柜中并实施双人管控，限制物理接触。同时启用操作系统层面的智能卡 PIN 锁定策略（连续输错 3 次锁定），作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.l0pht.com/advisories/etoken-piepa.txt","http://www.osvdb.org/3266","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/1170","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19894","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/b4f1378756fd26f414d09a97dc81126672830951/2000/CVE-2000-0427.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/24df5d59670dfe04b9c86de11fa86df63c0d28f7/cves/2000/0xxx/CVE-2000-0427.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-2000/CVE-2000-0427","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2000/CVE-2000-0427.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/2000/CVE-2000-0427.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/4544d3857250fe21711ce8febf38e8822729678f/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-3hmx-5jq6-252x/GHSA-3hmx-5jq6-252x.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/39f1db26eec9899ab2f8110ab3b45424c6fe9ec2/nvdcve/CVE-2000-0427.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_001350.txt","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idinfor"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2000/AVE-